#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "gzip"
msgstr "gzip"

#. Tag: author
#: index.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Lauri.Watts; &Lauri.Watts.mail;"
msgstr "&लौरी.वाट्स; &लौरी.वाट्स.मेल;"

#. Tag: trans_comment
#: index.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "ROLES_OF_TRANSLATORS"
msgstr "अनुवादकानां_भूमिका"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>gzip</command> is a compression program"
msgstr "<command>gzip</command> इति संपीडनकार्यक्रमः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The gzip KIO worker is not directly usable, and is intended for use as a "
"filter. For example, the tar KIO worker can filter a file through the gzip "
"KIO worker, in order to display the contents of a <literal role=\"extension"
"\">tar.gz</literal> file directly in a &konqueror; window."
msgstr ""
"gzip KIO कार्यकर्ता प्रत्यक्षतया उपयोगयोग्यः नास्ति, तथा च फ़िल्टररूपेण उपयोगाय अभिप्रेतः "
"। यथा, tar KIO कार्यकर्ता gzip KIO कार्यकर्तुः माध्यमेन सञ्चिकां छानयितुं शक्नोति, यत् "
"<literal role=\"extension\">tar.gz</literal> सञ्चिकायाः सामग्रीं प्रत्यक्षतया "
"&konqueror; कोष्ठ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you click on a file compressed with a <literal role=\"extension\">gz</"
"literal> extension in &konqueror;, this KIO worker is used to uncompress it "
"and display it as a normal (uncompressed) file."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् &konqueror;मध्ये <literal role=\"extension\">gz</literal> विस्तारेण सह "
"संपीडितां सञ्चिकां क्लिक् करोति तर्हि एतस्य KIO कार्यकर्तुः उपयोगः तस्याः असंपीडनार्थं "
"सामान्य (असंपीडित) सञ्चिकारूपेण प्रदर्शयितुं च उपयुज्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are a developer, and would like to use the gzip filter, you can find "
"documentation on using KIO workers at <ulink url=\"http://techbase.kde.org"
"\">http://techbase.kde.org</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् विकासकः अस्ति, तथा च gzip फ़िल्टरस्य उपयोगं कर्तुम् इच्छति, तर्हि भवान् <ulink "
"url=\"http://techbase.kde.org\">http://techbase.kde.org< इत्यत्र KIO कार्यकर्तृणां "
"उपयोगस्य दस्तावेजीकरणं प्राप्तुं शक्नोति /उलिंक्>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the manual: <ulink url=\"man:/gzip\">gzip</ulink>."
msgstr "पुस्तिकाम् पश्यन्तु: <ulink url=\"man:/gzip\">gzip</ulink> ।"
